reports.title: Traffic Accident on Highway A4
reports.summary: Multiple vehicle collision detected on Highway A4, km 36. Two cars involved, one possibly overturned.

reports.title: Building Fire in Downtown Area
reports.summary: Smoke and flames detected on the 3rd floor of apartment building on Kościuszki Street. No visible casualties.

reports.title: Medical Emergency in City Park
reports.summary: Person collapsed near the central fountain in Słodowa Park. Possible cardiac event.

reports.title: Fallen Tree Blocking Road
reports.summary: Large tree fallen across Powstańców Śląskich Street after storm. Two lanes blocked, no vehicles damaged.

reports.title: Chemical Spill Near Industrial Zone
reports.summary: Unknown substance leaking from tanker truck on Bierutowska Street. Creating vapor cloud, area needs evacuation.

reports.title: Water Main Break
reports.summary: Major flooding on Świdnicka Street due to broken water main. Water level rising, affecting local businesses.

reports.title: Gas Leak in Residential Area
reports.summary: Strong gas odor detected near apartment complex on Grabiszyńska Street. Potential hazard.
